# Onboarding — always applied

Before generating or scaffolding any code in a new/empty workspace, confirm the project's namespace
prefix (the `YourApp` placeholder) by asking the user one question — unless it is already given in the
prompt, the folder name, or an existing project. Then apply that name as you create files.

Full detail: [`agent-standards/05-onboarding.md`](../../agent-standards/05-onboarding.md).
